<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavarṣaṁbulu 
<lb n="2"/>1466 Agu krōdi saṁvvatsara 
<lb n="3"/>māgha śu 10 gu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī bhaṭṭara 
<lb n="4"/>dēvuninijaparikaramaina seṣaṁ 
<lb n="5"/>Abbayyaṁgāri priyasiṣyulaina <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> calla 
<lb n="6"/>tiṁmmāreḍḍikiṁnni tippaṁmmakuṁ jaṁnmiṁ 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ccina kumāruṁḍu koṁḍḍāreḍḍiṁ 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>nni <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> yiyyana pinataṁḍri ceṁnnāreḍḍikiṁnni pōtaṁ 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>mmakuṁnna suputṛlaina koṁḍḍayya kōnayya tiṁma 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>yannu tama sarimālagōtraṁ pāvanaṁ 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>gānu gōpināthaniki nagaru kaṭṭiṁcci pratiṣṭa 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>cēsiri Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigānu śrī <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

